text: Ryan Williams (born October 11, 1996) is an American soccer who plays as an attacking midfielder for New Mexico United in the USL Championship. ==Career== On January 9, 2019, USL Championship side New Mexico United announced they had signed Ryan Williams ahead of their inaugural 2019 season. ==References== ==External links== * * Profile at JBU Athletics Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Charlotte Eagles players Category:John Brown University alumni Category:New Mexico United players Category:People from Honolulu County, Hawaii Category:USL League Two players Category:USL Championship players Category:American soccer players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Soccer players from Hawaii
